textBeforeTable: Upcoming Test Dates   You can also explore our Resources page to check out our testing policies and calendar. Visit the Test Reporting Locations Map for driving directions to all on-campus testing locations. The Testing Center offers On-Campus Exams and Proctoring Services for various types of tests. Off-Campus Exams page provides information to tests that are not offered at CSUN. CSUN's Testing Center provides students, faculty, staff and the community with high-quality testing and instructional assessment services. The center follows the National College Testing Association (NCTA) Professional Standards and Guidelines, as well as governmental regulations that promote responsible fiscal, legal, ethical and equitable practices.
